these debt securities are included, net of applicable deferred income taxes, in equity (Accumulated other comprehensive
income (loss) in Statement 3). The unrealized gains and losses arising from the revaluation of the equity securities are included
in Other income (expense) in Statement 1. Realized gains and losses on sales of investments are generally determined using the
specific identification method for debt and equity securities and are included in Other income (expense) in Statement 1.
